					<h1>Expert Blog</h1>  
															        
					<div class="view view-blog-post view-id-blog_post view-display-id-page_1 view-dom-id-1">
        <div class="view-header">
      <p><em>ChinaFAQs experts react to the latest headlines about China climate and energy issues.</em></p>
    </div>
  
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first">
      
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/4217314587_fe63762b14.jpg" alt="" title="" width="180" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../reducing-greenhouse-gas-emissions-china-closes-highly-polluting-plants">Reducing Greenhouse Gas Emissions: China Closes Highly Polluting Plants</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-author-value">
          <label class="views-label-field-author-value">
        Posted by:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content">Deborah Seligsohn</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-created">
                <span class="field-content">August 11, 2010</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The big news this week is that <a href="http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jzjTKTihb71z71qb2u3L9SOk0HXg">China is removing outdated equipment from another 2000 plants</a>, and they are moving quite rapidly – the equipment is to be phased out by the end of September.   These closures are part of the tougher measures Premier Wen Jiabao <A href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../china-major-push-meet-20-energy-intensity-target">announced in April</a>.  While some have expressed <A href="http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2010/08/10/factory-closure-order-less-than-it-might-seem/">skepticism about this move</a>, because equipment rather than whole factories are being phased out, in fact, this looks to be a positive move. While China has made significant efficiency advances by closing whole factories, there is a limit to how many such highly inefficient factories actually exist.  As the very oldest, least efficient have been phased out, more sophisticated policies that pinpoint problematic equipment are needed.</p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-view-node">
                <span class="field-content"><div class="readmore"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../reducing-greenhouse-gas-emissions-china-closes-highly-polluting-plants">Read More</a></div></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-tid">
          <label class="views-label-tid">
        Issue Areas:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/energy-efficiency">Energy Efficiency</a>, <a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/industry">Industry</a>, <a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/policy-and-governance">Policy and Governance</a></span>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even">
      
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/oil_barrels_7-20-10.jpg" alt="" title="" width="180" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../china-tops-us-energy-use-become-worlds-top-energy-consumer">China Tops U.S. in Energy Use to Become World&#039;s Top Energy Consumer</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-author-value">
          <label class="views-label-field-author-value">
        Posted by:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content">Nick Price</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-created">
                <span class="field-content">July 20, 2010</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>China has passed the U.S. to become the world&#8217;s biggest energy consumer, according to new data from the <a href="http://www.iea.org/index_info.asp?id=1479">International Energy Agency</a>.  And while many expected China to overtake the U.S., most thought it wouldn&#8217;t be for another 5 years.</p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-view-node">
                <span class="field-content"><div class="readmore"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../china-tops-us-energy-use-become-worlds-top-energy-consumer">Read More</a></div></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-tid">
          <label class="views-label-tid">
        Issue Areas:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/energy-and-emissions-data">Energy and Emissions Data</a></span>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd">
      
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/al_gore_6-10-10.jpg" alt="" title="" width="108" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../climate-change-messengers-china-al-gore-brings-his-lecture-beijing">Climate Change Messengers in China: Al Gore Brings His Lecture to Beijing</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-author-value">
          <label class="views-label-field-author-value">
        Posted by:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content">Deborah Seligsohn</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-created">
                <span class="field-content">June 10, 2010</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Former Vice President Al Gore launched his Climate Project’s lecture program in Beijing June 10, personally devoting an entire day to training 300 Chinese in how to give his famous lecture.  The event was striking for the diversity and the quality of the participants.  His partners in China’s Ministry of Science and Technology and the China Agenda 21 Sustainable Development Office invited participants from all over China, including scholars, government officials, corporate middle managers, independent entrepreneurs, NGO staff and students.</p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-view-node">
                <span class="field-content"><div class="readmore"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../climate-change-messengers-china-al-gore-brings-his-lecture-beijing">Read More</a></div></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-tid">
          <label class="views-label-tid">
        Issue Areas:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/united-states-china-cooperation">United States-China Cooperation</a></span>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-4 views-row-even">
      
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/air_6-2-10.jpg" alt="" title="" width="159" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../cleaning-chinas-air-first-regional-air-quality-regulations">Cleaning China’s Air: First Regional Air Quality Regulations</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-author-value">
          <label class="views-label-field-author-value">
        Posted by:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content">Deborah Seligsohn</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-created">
                <span class="field-content">June 02, 2010</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>China’s State Council promulgated its first-ever regional air quality regulations on May 11. This is the first time outside of the special provisions for the Beijing Olympics and the Shanghai Expo that China has set up a structure for ensuring air quality across multiple provincial and urban jurisdictions involving entire airsheds.  These new regulations begin the process of institutionalizing the lessons learned during the major efforts to improve air quality for those headlining events and bringing those lessons learned both to the long-term health of those two regions and to other regions facing air quality challenges in China.  The full regulations are on line in Chinese at the <a href="http://zfs.mep.gov.cn/fg/gwyw/201005/t20100514_189497.htm">Ministry of Environmental Protection’s website</a> and our colleagues at the Energy Foundation’s Beijing office have helpfully translated them into English and allowed us to post the <a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../library/chinas-new-regional-air-quality-regulation-translated">English translation</a>.</p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-view-node">
                <span class="field-content"><div class="readmore"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../cleaning-chinas-air-first-regional-air-quality-regulations">Read More</a></div></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-tid">
          <label class="views-label-tid">
        Issue Areas:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/measurement-and-compliance">Measurement and Compliance</a>, <a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/policy-and-governance">Policy and Governance</a></span>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-5 views-row-odd">
      
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/flag_5_26_10.jpg" alt="" title="" width="200" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../us-china-strategic-and-economic-dialogue-pledges-greater-energy-market-transparency-and-e">US-China Strategic and Economic Dialogue: Pledges of Greater Energy Market Transparency and Energy Supply Diversification</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-author-value">
          <label class="views-label-field-author-value">
        Posted by:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content">Deborah Seligsohn</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-created">
                <span class="field-content">May 26, 2010</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Climate change was not the big news it was a year ago at the US-China Strategic and Economic Dialogue (S&amp;ED).  This is not surprising given that China made its major commitment on emissions reductions – its 40-45% carbon intensity target by 2020 – last year and US climate legislation is pending in the Senate.  But many of the key players on climate change, including Secretary of State Clinton, her Climate Negotiator Todd Stern, and Department of Energy Assistant Secretary David Sandalow, were at the meeting.   Energy Secretary Steven Chu stayed in the US to address the <a href="http://www.energy.gov/news/9001.htm">Gulf of Mexico oil spill</a>, but his Department co-hosted three major bilateral seminars on energy efficiency, renewable energy and biofuels after the S&amp;ED.</p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-view-node">
                <span class="field-content"><div class="readmore"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../us-china-strategic-and-economic-dialogue-pledges-greater-energy-market-transparency-and-e">Read More</a></div></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-tid">
          <label class="views-label-tid">
        Issue Areas:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/renewables-and-alternative-energy">Renewables and Alternative Energy</a>, <a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/united-states-china-cooperation">United States-China Cooperation</a></span>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-6 views-row-even">
      
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/smoke&#32;5-14-10.jpg" alt="" title="" width="160" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../new-approaches-climate-action-china-china-considers-carbon-tax-proposals">New Approaches to Climate Action in China: China Considers Carbon Tax Proposals</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-author-value">
          <label class="views-label-field-author-value">
        Posted by:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content">Deborah Seligsohn</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-created">
                <span class="field-content">May 14, 2010</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The concept of a carbon tax is receiving more and more attention in China, and there are even some formal proposals floating around the government.  It was discussed by Jiang Kejun of China’s Energy Research Institute at the recent <a href="http://finance.sina.com.cn/focus/10zglvgs/">China Green Enterprise Forum</a> and our network expert <a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../expert/bo-shen">Bo Shen</a> of the Lawrence Berkeley National Labs alerted us that both the Chinese and English versions of a newspaper article on the subject have now appeared on the National Development and Reform Commission’s (NDRC) <a href="www.ccchina.gov.cn">climate change website</a>. The <a href="http://www.ccchina.gov.cn/cn/NewsInfo.asp?NewsId=23889">Chinese article</a> gives more detail than the <a href="http://www.ccchina.gov.cn/en/NewsInfo.asp?NewsId=23899">English article</a> and quotes unnamed officials from the Ministry of Finance (MOF) and the State Tax Bureau as well.</p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-view-node">
                <span class="field-content"><div class="readmore"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../new-approaches-climate-action-china-china-considers-carbon-tax-proposals">Read More</a></div></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-tid">
          <label class="views-label-tid">
        Issue Areas:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/energy-efficiency">Energy Efficiency</a>, <a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../category/issue-areas/policy-and-governance">Policy and Governance</a></span>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="views-row views-row-7 views-row-odd">
      
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/dam&#32;5-10-10.jpg" alt="" title="" width="150" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../india-china-climate-cooperation-thrives-spirit-copenhagen">India-China Climate Cooperation Thrives with the “Spirit of Copenhagen”</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-author-value">
          <label class="views-label-field-author-value">
        Posted by:
      </label>
                <span class="field-content">Deborah Seligsohn</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-created">
                <span class="field-content">May 10, 2010</span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Indian Environment Minister Jairam Ramesh described the “Copenhagen Spirit” as substantially improving ties between China and India and leading to improved cooperation in related environmental areas, including hydrographic data, glaciological research and forestry.  He expressed hope that an MOU signed last fall on energy technologies would yield some concrete projects, but admitted those opportunities had yet to be explored.</p></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-view-node">
                <span class="field-content"><div class="readmore"><a href="../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../../india-china-climate-cooperation-thrives-spirit-copenhagen">Read More</a></div></span>
  </div>
  
